# HEA melt-solidify workflow skeleton
units           metal
dimension       3
boundary        p p p
atom_style      atomic

read_data       data.hea

pair_style      eam/alloy
pair_coeff      * * potential.eam.alloy E1 E2 E3 E4 E5

variable        T_init equal 300
variable        T_melt equal 2200
variable        T_melt_hold equal 2200
variable        T_quench equal 300

thermo          100
thermo_style    custom step temp pe ke etotal press vol

timestep        0.001

# Add staged heating, hold, and cooling blocks.
# Confirm whether a separate relaxation stage is required.
